Attributes 

these are optional
using these we can provide additional information to HTML elements
combination of name & value pairs
for a single element we may multiple attributes.


<tag_name  name="value" > .....  </tag_name>


align   // left, right, center
title // "user defined string"
style // Allows to write inline CSS for an element

html - dir //  ltr (default value) & rtl - is used for arabic languages

html - lang // en, fr ... 


Boolean Attributes

disabled
readonly
required
autocomplete


Generic Attributes

align / horizontally aligns tags // right, left, center
valign / vertically aligns tags //  top, middle, bottom
bgcolor / backgroud color // #000000  
width // we can provide width fo that element
height // we can provide height fo that element
title // pop-up  || tool-tip info about that elemt


backgroud /  url // this places background image 

id // used for styling
class // used for styling
